      • getFirstPOSTags

        public edu.jhu.hlt.concrete.TokenTagging getFirstPOSTags(edu.jhu.hlt.concrete.Tokenization tokenization)
                                                  throws ConcreteException
        Find the first POS tagging (TokenTagging.taggingType == POS) in the given Tokenization. This throws a ConcreteException if no POS taggings are found. Note that this is only to be used when the exact POS theory doesn't matter, or when the caller is sure that there is only one POS theory.
        Throws:
        ConcreteException
